title: Banged Up S01E01 WS PDTV XVID
description:
CH5 21.00-22.00 7th July 2008 

Banged Up S01E01 

Documentary series presented by David Blunkett MP in which ten youths spend ten days in prison. Each of the teenagers has convictions ranging from theft to assault, but none of them have ever served time behind bars. In a unique experiment, they will find out what life in prison is truly like for the first time - but will it be enough to change their ways? In the opening instalment, the youths arrive at Scarborough Prison and face a tough time settling in to their new routine.
